{"tid":444104,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"標準家用計算方法","createTime":"2017-10-22T08:18:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T08:12:07.000Z","uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1b9219f8053d3b2c728aec2906132571264bc1e9","tid":444104,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T08:18:58.000Z","msg":"每月留份最少等於標準最低工資嘅錢俾自己買野就係標準<br />\n所以收入連兩份標準最低工資都冇嘅咪撚俾家用<br />\n<br />\n標準最低工資 = 最低工資 x 8 x 22 (以五天工作日,每日8小時為準)<br />\n今年係HK$6072,兩份就係HK$12144<br />\n就算高過都頂多俾剩低果D算啦,最盡俾餘額50%/標準最低工資,以較低為準"},{"pid":"8b73d6230578c67f8db3d4d0a2128ddac30d9bab","tid":444104,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T23:14:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f3e720921d57fada96698180bd9c20bf8ad380","tid":444104,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T23:26:41.000Z","msg":"住自己屋企例外<br />\n唔俾家用俾人踢出街<br />\n住出面無2萬學咩人俾家用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係租都6k 駛用又6k<br />\n得8k可以真正自己用 當儲4k<br />\n得返4k 咁就可以唸俾1-2k家用<br />\n<br />\n如果住屋企就俾4-5k基本"},{"pid":"f99ec91a09b9907c2402b41d648f4e9a95b68663","tid":444104,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T23:41:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>住自己屋企例外<br />\n唔俾家用俾人踢出街<br />\n住出面無2萬學咩人俾家用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係租都6k 駛用又6k<br />\n得8k可以真正自己用 當儲4k<br />\n得返4k 咁就可以唸俾1-2k家用<br />\n<br />\n如果住屋企就俾4-5k基本</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搵9k住屋企個d 俾3k<br />\n再多你就一世住屋企<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n住屋企你就當租出面既套房<br />\n4k一個月<br />\n俾唔俾多d就睇你自己搵幾多<br />\n<br />\n住出面<br />\n高過30k就1/10至1/7<br />\n唔好俾太多<br />\n為自己唸"},{"pid":"ed2ce968c7a3aaa4992de269450254a06e5bf079","tid":444104,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:36:56.000Z","msg":"搵9k仲要俾3k?連生存都成問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ada0562a0b716f9aeb736b480ef75bef92a111b","tid":444104,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T05:34:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵9k仲要俾3k?連生存都成問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔俾要訓街wow<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你訓到咪唔俾lol<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e527a280b0579c066e329ad2ba0a3aab5c4d5c22","tid":444104,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T05:11:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搵9k仲要俾3k?連生存都成問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔俾要訓街wow<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你訓到咪唔俾lol<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔通冇工開又要訓街?<br />\n一係搵撚過份工啦,咪撚搞到自己生存都唔